sentences: Lateef Daumont, better known by his stage name Lateef the Truthspeaker, or mononymously as Lateef, is a hip hop artist from Oakland, California.
He has released several mixtapes such as Ahead of the Curve (2007), Truth Is Love (2009), and Truth at Sea (2011).
His solo debut album, Firewire, was released in 2011.
He was also featured on the songs "Wonderful Night" and "That Old Pair of Jeans" by Fatboy Slim.
